## 9. When Running Code

### Local Development
```bash
# Start database
docker-compose up -d postgres

# Run migrations
python -m src.database

# Run bot
python -m src.bot.main

# Run admin (different terminal)
python -m src.admin.main
```

### Testing
```bash
# Run tests
pytest tests/

# Run specific test
pytest tests/test_user_service.py::test_create_user
```

### Check Code Quality
```bash
# Format code
black src/

# Type checking
mypy src/

# Linting
flake8 src/
```

