## 13. Configuration (.env)

Required values:
```
BOT_TOKEN=your_rubika_token
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@localhost/rubifo
ZARINPAL_MERCHANT_ID=your_merchant_id
ADMIN_USERNAME=admin
ADMIN_PASSWORD_HASH=bcrypted_hash
```

Use in code:
```python
from src.config import BOT_TOKEN, DATABASE_URL, ...
```

