## Summary

```
✅ DO: Async, type hints, docstrings, services, error handling
❌ DON'T: Sync, no hints, no docs, handlers with logic, global state
📁 LOCATION: Use correct folder structure
🧪 TEST: Write tests with code
📝 COMMIT: Clear messages with T##
🚀 DEPLOY: Follow deployment process
```

